summary: Replaces the creepy wooden texture of the Manniquins with the Imperial Skin.
descriptionHtml:
From the first time I saw the Mannequins in the game I was very creeped out by the way they look so I creaded this small mod to make them look like the default male imperial.  (Now with Female Imperial and Male Nord)

This is the first time I have even looked at creating a mod but after I saw that someone has done the same thing with the female for a house mod I figured it must be possible to do with a male.  It took me several hours to figure it out (and learn the construciton kit) and it ended up being very simple but if I messed up anything along the way then let me know and I will try to fix it.

NOTE:  This does not contain any nudity but if you have a skin replacer than the Mannequins will be nude as well.  As it is alone it simply looks like an Imperial male in his underwear standing in your home untill you put armor on it.

Installation:  Just copy ONE of the files into your Skyrim/Data folder and then check the esp in the mod activation section.
author: devin77536
